Is e buidheann de eileanan a tha ann an '''Svalbard'''.
Tha iad anns a’ [[Cuan Argtach|Chuan Argtach]] eadar [[Nirribhidh]] agus a’ [[Phòla-a-Tuath]], eadar 76° gu  81° Tuath agus 10° gu 35° Ear.
Tha iad pairt den [[Nirribhidh]] tron  ''"Svalbard Treaty"'' , ach ann an doigh sònraichte. Mar sin is e Svalbard aon de na ceithir dùthchanan air feadh [[an t-Saoghal]] ris an canar: ''Special entities whose status is recognized by international treaty''.

Tha dìreach trì eileanan ann far a bheil daoine a’ fuireach. Is iad: Spitsbergen, Bjørnøya agus Hopen.

Is e [[Longyearbyen]] ann an Spitsbergen  an t-àite as motha ann an Svalbard.

